OL,5, A mayor has defended launching a       
OL,6, fundraising page to cover the fine of a
OL,7, man who threatened a child.            
OL,9,FBernard John Higgins, from Hemlington, 
OL,10,Fwas convicted at Teesside Magistrates' 
OL,11,FCourt after confronting a boy allegedly
OL,12,Fresponsible for causing trouble on the 
OL,13,F65-year-old's estate.                  
OL,15,FMiddlesbrough mayor Andy Preston asked 
OL,16,Fpeople to donate #1 each towards the   
OL,17,F#107 Mr Higgins was ordered to pay.    
OL,19,FHe said it had been "wrong" for the    
OL,20,Fpensioner to be prosecuted.            
